Customs officials inspect hundreds of school buses at a port in Qingdao, East China's Shandong Province on Saturday. The buses, made by a Chinese company, will be shipped to Saudi Arabia after customs registration. China has seen a rapid increase in school bus orders from countries and regions along the routes of the Belt and Road Initiative in recent years. Photo: VCG  
